<!doctype html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Diagnóstico Técnico | APP CARACTERIZAÇÃO DE SOLO NB</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0b1020;
      --panel: #121933;
      --panel-2: #182142;
      --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      --text: #edf2ff;
      --muted: #b7c2e0;
      --accent: #4ea1ff;
      --ok: #18a957;
      --warn: #d6a400;
      --crit: #d64545;
      --chip: #22305f;
      --shadow: 0 10px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.30);
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #09101d 0%, #0d1530 100%);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    }

    .wrap {
      max-width: 1400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(78,161,255,0.18), rgba(255,255,255,0.04));
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 24px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      margin: 0 0 8px 0;
      font-size: 28px;
    }

    .hero p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .card {
      background: rgba(18,25,51,0.95);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .card-header {
      padding: 16px 18px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .card-body {
      padding: 18px;
    }

    textarea {
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 520px;
      resize: vertical;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: #09101d;
      color: var(--text);
      padding: 16px;
      font-family: Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.45;
      outline: none;
    }

    .actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 14px;
    }

    button {
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: white;
      background: #235dbe;
      transition: transform 0.15s ease, opacity 0.15s ease;
    }

    button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      opacity: 0.95;
    }

    button.secondary {
      background: #2a345a;
    }

    button.success {
      background: #157347;
    }

    button.warning {
      background: #8a6b00;
    }

    .statusbar {
      margin-top: 12px;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: var(--muted);
      min-height: 46px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .kpis {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .kpi {
      background: var(--panel-2);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 14px;
    }

    .kpi .label {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    .kpi .value {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .section {
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 14px;
    }

    .section h3 {
      margin: 0 0 12px 0;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .chips {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .chip {
      padding: 7px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--chip);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .chip.ok { background: rgba(24,169,87,0.18); }
    .chip.warn { background: rgba(214,164,0,0.18); }
    .chip.crit { background: rgba(214,69,69,0.18); }

    pre {
      background: #09101d;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 14px;
      overflow: auto;
      color: #dce6ff;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      white-space: pre-wrap;
      word-break: break-word;
    }

    .list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .item {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 12px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    }

    .item strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1080px) {
      .grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      textarea {
        min-height: 380px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <section class="hero">
      <h1>Diagnóstico Técnico Aplicado</h1>
      <p>
        Ambiente separado para validar o núcleo normativo, análise automática, workflow e auditoria
        sem interferir no fluxo principal já homologado do APP CARACTERIZAÇÃO DE SOLO NB.
      </p>
    </section>

    <div class="grid">
      <section class="card">
        <div class="card-header">Contexto do Projeto (JSON)</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <textarea id="jsonInput" spellcheck="false"></textarea>

          <div class="actions">
            <button id="btnLoadExample" class="secondary">Carregar exemplo</button>
            <button id="btnRun">Executar análise técnica</button>
            <button id="btnDownloadJson" class="success">Baixar resultado JSON</button>
            <button id="btnDownloadTxt" class="warning">Baixar relatório TXT</button>
          </div>

          <div id="statusbar" class="statusbar">Aguardando execução.</div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="card">
        <div class="card-header">Resultado consolidado</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="kpis">
            <div class="kpi">
              <div class="label">Ocorrências</div>
              <div id="kpiTotal" class="value">0</div>
            </div>
            <div class="kpi">
              <div class="label">Status sugerido</div>
              <div id="kpiStatus" class="value">-</div>
            </div>
            <div class="kpi">
              <div class="label">Emissão</div>
              <div id="kpiEmit" class="value">-</div>
            </div>
            <div class="kpi">
              <div class="label">Bloqueantes</div>
              <div id="kpiBlock" class="value">0</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="section">
            <h3>Severidade</h3>
            <div id="severityChips" class="chips"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="section">
            <h3>Texto técnico sugerido</h3>
            <pre id="textSuggestions">Sem dados.</pre>
          </div>

          <div class="section">
            <h3>Achados e recomendações</h3>
            <div id="findingsList" class="list"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="section">
            <h3>Workflow + auditoria</h3>
            <pre id="workflowOutput">Sem dados.</pre>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script type="module" src="./dev/diagnostico-tecnico.js"></script>
</body>
</html>

